{
  "stem": "893.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said he wasn't baptized, that he's Roman Catholic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took him down-- the German fellow told him to take him down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, at that point, I knew that-- that he'll-- he won't come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I sort of-- when they grabbed him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called one of the Slovakian guards to take him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, he didn't put up any resistance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He still hoped, you know, who knows, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe-- maybe they'll just look at the paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they'll call the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they examined him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that point, I wanted to get up and sort of give myself up, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt, I'll go with him, you know-- whatever, whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was-- wasn't-- maybe it wouldn't have been a wise decision.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father gave me a stern look, you know, like, you know, don't-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] don't move.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I stayed there, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I sort of felt, you know, maybe I should go back to my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I felt sort of-- and I still, up today, I feel bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe I should've gone with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe I would have been next to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's true, he got sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He contacted [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] typhus, and he-- he died in [NON-ENGLISH] I believe, in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- in March of '45, so I was told.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I still feel bad, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe I could have-- had I been with him-- [PAUSES FOR 15 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I would have helped him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Well, that's, you know-- that was the end of-- when I got to Bratislava, I went to the Jewish area there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I saw there were no Jews there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
